These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, purple
2 different pets are kept: turtle, dog
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, bike
1. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk      | fanta    |
| Color           | purple | orange |
| Pet   | turtle       | dog  |
| Transport     | airplane      | bike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, watermelon
City: nizza, prague
2 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, march
1. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | watermelon | cauliflower |
| City   | nizza       | prague         |
| Pet           | rabbit     | cat         |
| Birthday     | march    | september    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, hiking
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, project-manager
House: ranch-style, art-deco
2 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg
1. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the analyst##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | hiking          | board-games |
| Job           | project-manager | analyst     |
| House   | ranch-style            | art-deco         |
| Game     | mah-jongg         | poker   |

