The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, epic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, trance
There are 2 different favourite colors: ebony, amber
1. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
2. the person playing scrabble is the person who likes ebony##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Game      | scrabble     | canasta   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | action |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | trance |
| Color           | ebony | amber    |

