.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, comedy
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, december
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, jazz
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, taxi
1. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of folk is the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Movie-Genre      | comedy     | musical |
| Birthday          | december   | september |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | folk     |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi     |

 